5 rooms from 16 m² to 28 m² with private bathroom, TV Wi-Fi, private terrace, swimming pool, sauna, rowing machine, indoor bike, private parking.
A 5-minute drive from Aix-en-Provence, between the city and the exceptional natural site of Mont Sainte-Victoire.
